  "original_title": "\u0db0\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca\u0da7 \u0db7\u0dd6\u0db8\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dca \u0d89\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2 \u0daf\u0dd2\u0db1 \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dba\u0dda\u0daf\u0dd3",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Kerosene to Dhivar in next few days",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Minister of Fisheries Douglas Devananda made a special statement to the media from Jaffna today (18th) that the unloading of the imported crude oil ship is currently taking place and after unloading and refining it, steps will be taken to provide all the fuel including kerosene needed by the Dhiwara community in this country in the next few days. He said while doing it.",
        "The Minister said that he and the President understand the suffering of the fishermen who have been suffering without fuel for many months, but this situation has arisen due to the country facing a big economic challenge and asks the entire fishing community to be patient for a few more days and after refining the crude oil vessel He said that it will be possible to fulfill the fuel needs of the community.",
        "Further, the Minister further said that arrangements are being made to bring fuel to the fishing community by the private sector and after receiving it, the fishing community will not have any fuel problem."
      ],
